Hypertrons-crx aims at tracing and digging GitHub projects and developers。We do this by inserting useful dashboards into some GitHub pages to help users gain the insight into developers and projects quickly. 

 Hypertrons-crx 用于 GitHub 项目与开发者关系的追踪、挖掘与洞察。通过可视化图表展示各类丰富的行为数据，方便用户快速洞察开发者与项目相关信息。
